---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms & Conditions — ScandiJapandi" description="Purchase terms, return policy, and consumer rights for ScandiJapandi customers.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-paper px-6 py-32 pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone mb-6">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-ink font-light mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone font-light mb-16">
        Last updated: July 2026 · SKM Nordic AS · Norway · Org.nr: [FYLL INN]
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-sm text-stone font-light leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">1. About us</h2>
          <p>ScandiJapandi is operated by SKM Nordic AS, a Norwegian limited company. Our registered address is [ADRESSE]. We can be reached at <a href="mailto:hello@scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">hello@scandijapandi.no</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">2. Orders and payment</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p>— All prices are listed in Norwegian Kroner (NOK) and include any applicable taxes where required by law.</p>
            <p>— Payment is processed securely by Stripe. We accept Visa, Mastercard, Klarna, and Link.</p>
            <p>— An order is confirmed when you receive an order confirmation email from us.</p>
            <p>— We reserve the right to cancel orders in cases of pricing errors, stock issues, or suspected fraud.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">3. Delivery</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p>— Delivery times and shipping costs are listed on our <a href="/shipping" class="text-ink underline">Shipping page</a>.</p>
            <p>— We are not responsible for delays caused by customs, weather, or carrier issues outside our control.</p>
            <p>— Risk of loss passes to the customer upon handover to the carrier.</p>
            <p>— Import duties and local taxes for international orders are the responsibility of the recipient.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">4. Right of withdrawal (EU/Norway)</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p>— Under Norwegian and EU consumer law (Angrerettloven), you have the right to withdraw from a purchase within <strong class="text-ink font-normal">14 days</strong> of receiving your order, without giving a reason.</p>
            <p>— To exercise this right, notify us by email at <a href="mailto:hello@scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">hello@scandijapandi.no</a> before the 14-day period expires.</p>
            <p>— Items must be returned unused, in original condition and packaging.</p>
            <p>— We will refund the full order value including original shipping within 14 days of receiving the returned item.</p>
            <p>— Return shipping costs are paid by the customer unless the item is faulty.</p>
            <p>— Custom, personalised, or perishable items are exempt from the right of withdrawal.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">5. Japanese consumer rights (特定商取引法)</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p>Under Japan's Act on Specified Commercial Transactions (特定商取引法に基づく表記):</p>
            <p>— 販売業者: SKM Nordic AS</p>
            <p>— 所在地: [ADRESSE], Norway</p>
            <p>— 電話番号: メールにてお問い合わせください</p>
            <p>— メールアドレス: hello@scandijapandi.no</p>
            <p>— 販売価格: 各商品ページに表示</p>
            <p>— 送料: 別途。<a href="/shipping" class="text-ink underline">配送情報ページ</a>をご確認ください</p>
            <p>— お支払い方法: クレジットカード（Stripe経由）、Klarna</p>
            <p>— 商品の引渡し時期: ご注文確認後7〜14営業日</p>
            <p>— 返品・交換: 商品到着後14日以内。未使用・未開封に限る</p>
            <p>— 不良品: 不良品の場合は全額返金または交換対応</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">6. Faulty items</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p>— If you receive a faulty or damaged item, contact us within 7 days of delivery with photos of the damage.</p>
            <p>— We will arrange a replacement or full refund at no cost to you.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">7. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All content on scandijapandi.no — including text, images, and design — is owned by SKM Nordic AS or licensed from our producers. Reproduction without permission is prohibited.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">8. Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by Norwegian law. Disputes shall be resolved in Norwegian courts, unless mandatory consumer protection laws in your country of residence provide otherwise.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink font-light mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any questions: <a href="mailto:hello@scandijapandi.no" class="text-ink underline">hello@scandijapandi.no</a></p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/8 flex flex-wrap gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone hover:text-ink transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/shipping" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone hover:text-ink transition-colors">Shipping Information</a>
        <a href="/" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-stone hover:text-ink transition-colors">← Back to collection</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
